Subject: [PATCH 0/9] Xiaomi Mi 8 (dipper) Mobian/mainline support
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add Mobian/mainline support for the Xiaomi Mi 8 (codename "dipper"),
a SDM845-based smartphone.

This series brings up:

  - display (Samsung EA8074 DSI command-mode AMOLED)
  - touchscreen (FTM5 / STMicro fts) on the Mobian carry driver
  - rear main camera (Sony IMX363)
  - audio (WCD9340 codec, TAS2557 speaker amp, q6voice path)
  - Wi-Fi (ath10k WCN3990), Bluetooth (WCN3990 UART6)
  - modem data, SMS and voice calls
  - USB-C / Type-C / USB-PD via the PMI8998 TCPM driver
    (added in a companion tcpm-pmi8998 series; the dipper DT
    enables it through the connector subnode + sink-vdos identity)
  - UFS storage, GPU (A630)
  - fuel gauge, charger and volume keys

Patches 1-3 are fixes for the Mobian carry FTM5 touchscreen driver;
patches 4-5 add the Samsung EA8074 panel driver and binding; patch 6
reorders the IMX363 power-on sequence to match the Sony datasheet;
patch 7 adds the TAS2557 ASoC driver; patches 8-9 add the dipper
board DT and enable the required driver modules in sdm845_defconfig.

Build note: the board DTS references PMI8998 Type-C/VBUS nodes
from the companion tcpm-pmi8998 series. Apply tcpm-pmi8998 first,
or apply both series before building the dipper DTB.

Tested on the "Dipper new MP v2.1" board variant with the p0 camera
pinout and a Semco-packaged IMX363 rear sensor. Other Mi 8 board or
camera variants may need DTS changes.

Base: Mobian linux-6.12-sdm845 6.12.91-1 (linux-6.12.91 with the
Mobian patch stack applied). This series does not apply on top of a
vanilla linux-6.12.91 tree: it depends on the Mobian carry FTM5
driver, IMX363 driver, and several Mobian sdm845 DT and config
patches being already present.

This patch set is intended for Mobian salsa MR review before going
through the more granular upstream process (mainline send-email for
the parts that fit, downstream carry for the rest).

Max Furman (9):
  Input: touchscreen/stm/ftm5: throttle zero-pressure warning
  Input: touchscreen/stm/ftm5: request IRQ with NO_AUTOEN
  Input: touchscreen/stm/ftm5: allow board to narrow active scan mask
  dt-bindings: display: panel: Add Samsung EA8074
  drm/panel: samsung: Add driver for Samsung EA8074
  media: i2c: imx363: start MCLK before supplies
  ASoC: codecs: add TAS2557 smart amplifier driver
  arm64: dts: qcom: add Xiaomi Mi 8 (dipper)
  arm64: configs: sdm845: enable Mi 8 (dipper) driver modules

